[% META
    title = "Managing Inventory Items"
    description = "Overview of inventory items, including their fields, configuration, and shop settings."
    roles = "admin"
    TemplateType = "Documentation"
    category = "Inventory"
    page_version = "1.00"
    last_updated = "2026-04-17"
    site_specific = "false"
%]
[% PageVersion = 'Documentation/Inventory/items.tt v1.00 2026-04-17' %]
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %][% PageVersion %][% END %]

<div class="container">
    <h1 style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--header-font)">Managing Inventory Items</h1>
    <div class="last-updated" style="color:var(--text-muted-color);font-size:var(--font-size-small)">Last Updated: 2026-04-17 | Version: 1.00 | Audience: Site Administrators</div>

    <!-- TOC -->
    <div id="toc" class="row" style="margin:var(--spacing-large) 0;background-color:var(--light-color);padding:var(--spacing-medium);border-left:4px solid var(--primary-color);border-radius:4px">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--header-font);margin-top:0">Quick Navigation</h2>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:var(--spacing-small)">
                <a href="#overview" style="color:var(--link-color);text-decoration:none;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:3px;background-color:var(--secondary-color);display:inline-block">Overview</a>
                <a href="#fields" style="color:var(--link-color);text-decoration:none;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:3px;background-color:var(--secondary-color);display:inline-block">Item Fields</a>
                <a href="#coa" style="color:var(--link-color);text-decoration:none;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:3px;background-color:var(--secondary-color);display:inline-block">COA Accounts</a>
                <a href="#shop" style="color:var(--link-color);text-decoration:none;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:3px;background-color:var(--secondary-color);display:inline-block">Shop Fields</a>
                <a href="#adding-editing" style="color:var(--link-color);text-decoration:none;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:3px;background-color:var(--secondary-color);display:inline-block">Adding & Editing</a>
                <a href="#tips" style="color:var(--link-color);text-decoration:none;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:3px;background-color:var(--secondary-color);display:inline-block">Tips</a>
                <a href="#troubleshooting" style="color:var(--link-color);text-decoration:none;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:3px;background-color:var(--secondary-color);display:inline-block">Troubleshooting</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="overview" class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--header-font)">Overview</h2>
            <p style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--body-font)">Inventory items are the fundamental building blocks of the Comserv inventory system. They represent everything from raw materials like filament and office supplies to finished products such as 3D prints, honey, or equipment. They are universal across the system and can be tracked, sold, or used in assemblies.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:right"><a href="#toc" style="color:var(--link-color);font-size:var(--font-size-small)">↑ Back to Top</a></p>

    <div id="fields" class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--header-font)">Item Fields Explained</h2>
            <ul style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--body-font)">
                <li><strong>SKU:</strong> A unique identifier for the item per site.</li>
                <li><strong>Name:</strong> The descriptive name of the item.</li>
                <li><strong>Category:</strong> Groups items for filtering and reporting.</li>
                <li><strong>Origin/How-made:</strong> Defines the source of the item (e.g., 3d_printed, grown, foraged, purchased, manufactured, overhead).</li>
                <li><strong>Unit of Measure:</strong> The standard unit for the item (e.g., each, g, kg, hr).</li>
                <li><strong>Unit Cost:</strong> What the site pays to acquire or produce the item.</li>
                <li><strong>Unit Price:</strong> The retail price at which the item is sold.</li>
                <li><strong>Barcode:</strong> For scanning and quick identification.</li>
                <li><strong>Status:</strong> Marks the item as Active or Inactive.</li>
                <li><strong>Assemblable Flag:</strong> Marks the item as a BOM parent (e.g., a 3D print made from filament).</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:right"><a href="#toc" style="color:var(--link-color);font-size:var(--font-size-small)">↑ Back to Top</a></p>

    <div id="coa" class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--header-font)">COA Account Fields</h2>
            <p style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--body-font)">Each item must be linked to the Chart of Accounts (COA) for proper financial tracking:</p>
            <ul style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--body-font)">
                <li><strong>inventory_accno_id:</strong> Asset account where stock value is held.</li>
                <li><strong>income_accno_id:</strong> Sales revenue account for when the item is sold.</li>
                <li><strong>expense_accno_id:</strong> COGS (Cost of Goods Sold) or expense account.</li>
                <li><strong>returns_accno_id:</strong> Account for handling returns and credits.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:right"><a href="#toc" style="color:var(--link-color);font-size:var(--font-size-small)">↑ Back to Top</a></p>

    <div id="shop" class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--header-font)">Shop Fields</h2>
            <p style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--body-font)">Controls how items appear to the public in the site shop:</p>
            <ul style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--body-font)">
                <li><strong>show_in_shop:</strong> Admin-only toggle to control public visibility.</li>
                <li><strong>hide_stock_count:</strong> Useful for print-on-demand items where physical stock isn't kept.</li>
                <li><strong>shop_options:</strong> JSON field for dynamic options like colour choosers.</li>
                <li><strong>image_path:</strong> Selected via the FileManager for product display.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:right"><a href="#toc" style="color:var(--link-color);font-size:var(--font-size-small)">↑ Back to Top</a></p>

    <div id="adding-editing" class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--header-font)">Adding & Editing</h2>
            <ul style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--body-font)">
                <li><strong>Add New Item:</strong> Navigate to <code>/Inventory/item/add</code>.</li>
                <li><strong>Edit Item:</strong> Use <code>/Inventory/item/edit/:id</code> for core fields or <code>/shop/admin/edit/:id</code> for shop-specific fields.</li>
                <li><strong>Item List:</strong> Access <code>/Inventory/items</code> to search and filter by category or status.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:right"><a href="#toc" style="color:var(--link-color);font-size:var(--font-size-small)">↑ Back to Top</a></p>

    <div id="tips" class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--header-font)">Tips</h2>
            <ul style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--body-font)">
                <li>Filament items should have <code>show_in_shop = 0</code> as they are raw materials, not products for sale.</li>
                <li>Print-on-demand items should use <code>hide_stock_count = 1</code> to avoid showing zero inventory to customers.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:right"><a href="#toc" style="color:var(--link-color);font-size:var(--font-size-small)">↑ Back to Top</a></p>

    <div id="troubleshooting" class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--header-font)">Troubleshooting</h2>
            <ul style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--body-font)">
                <li><strong>"Field doesn't have a default value":</strong> A required field was left blank during item creation.</li>
                <li><strong>"Ambiguous column":</strong> This indicates a table join bug; ensure you are using the latest version.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:right"><a href="#toc" style="color:var(--link-color);font-size:var(--font-size-small)">↑ Back to Top</a></p>

    <!-- SEE ALSO at bottom -->
    <div id="see-also" style="background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-left:4px solid var(--success-color);padding:var(--spacing-medium);border-radius:4px;margin:var(--spacing-medium) 0">
        <h2 style="color:var(--success-color);font-family:var(--header-font);margin-top:0">See Also</h2>
        <ul style="color:var(--text-color);font-family:var(--body-font)">
            <li><a href="/Documentation/Inventory/index" style="color:var(--link-color)">Inventory System Overview</a></li>
            <li><a href="/Documentation/Inventory/stock" style="color:var(--link-color)">Stock Level Management</a></li>
            <li><a href="/Documentation/Inventory/bom" style="color:var(--link-color)">Bill of Materials (BOM)</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
